RebelPremonition:
SpawnReinforcements(RebelScoutSpawn)
ENUN
MOVE 10 Rebel [20,6]
ENUN
CameraCursor(Rebel)
Text(ChA4RebelPremonitionText1)
MOVE 20 Rebel [23,11]
ENUN
REMOVEUNIT Rebel
